Depends: libbitcoin-blockchain (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Asynchronous C++ Bitcoin library - development files
 libbitcoin-blockchain is a Bitcoin blockchain library.
 .
 This package provides the development files (ie. includes, static library),
 that allow to build software which uses libbitcoin-blockchain.

